      <title>特朗普的现金储备面临 4.5 亿美元双重判决的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-29/trump-s-cash-stockpile-at-risk-from-450-million-dual-verdicts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普在纽约面临两项重大法律判决，这些判决有可能消灭大多数人——如果不是全部的话——这位亿万富翁声称他手头有大量现金，这对这位与财务成功和财富息息相关的总统候选人来说是一个潜在的打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-29/trump-s-cash-stockpile-at-risk-from-450-million-dual-verdicts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 00:49:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美军阵亡后拜登面临对抗伊朗的压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/biden-faces-pressure-to-confront-iran-after-us-troops-killed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在伊朗的代理人在约旦的一次无人机袭击中杀死三名美国士兵后，总统乔·拜登面临着与伊朗直接对抗的越来越大的压力，这恰恰冒着他所说的他希望避免的更广泛的地区冲突的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/biden-faces-pressure-to-confront-iran-after-us-troops-killed</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 23:46:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马丘比丘铁路工人抗议导致数百名游客滞留</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/machu-picchu-railway-worker-protest-strands-hundreds-of-tourists</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于铁路工人继续抗议新的票务系统，通往秘鲁马丘比丘的火车线路已关闭，直至另行通知。自 1 月 20 日抗议活动开始以来，已有数百名游客被困。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/machu-picchu-railway-worker-protest-strands-hundreds-of-tourists</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 23:34:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚造王者敦促反对派停止削弱安华</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/malaysian-kingmaker-urges-opposition-to-stop-undercutting-anwar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚总理安瓦尔·易卜拉欣脆弱的执政联盟的主要支持者敦促该国政界人士停止破坏政府，认为该国需要政治稳定才能专注于紧迫的经济挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/malaysian-kingmaker-urges-opposition-to-stop-undercutting-anwar</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国将禁止一次性电子烟以保护儿童健康</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/uk-to-ban-disposable-vapes-in-bid-to-protect-children-s-health</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国将禁止使用一次性电子烟，以在年轻人使用电子烟激增的情况下保护儿童健康。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/uk-to-ban-disposable-vapes-in-bid-to-protect-children-s-health</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 22:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马科斯推动菲律宾团结，杜特尔特猛烈抨击继任者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/marcos-calls-for-unity-as-duterte-s-son-seeks-his-resignation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯和他的前任罗德里戈·杜特尔特分别举行集会，吸引了数千名支持者，凸显了日益加深的分歧，可能会导致赢得 2022 年大选的该国最有权势的政治家族联盟的分裂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/marcos-calls-for-unity-as-duterte-s-son-seeks-his-resignation</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 16:35:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国和中国官员将就芬太尼打击问题举行会晤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/us-chinese-officials-to-meet-on-fentanyl-crackdown-on-jan-30</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府高级官员表示，美国和中国官员将于北京会面，讨论打击致命合成药物芬太尼非法贩运的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-28/us-chinese-officials-to-meet-on-fentanyl-crackdown-on-jan-30</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 14:12:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰腐败官员盗走4000万美元用于购买俄罗斯战争武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-01-28/ukraine-says-corrupt-officials-stole-40-million-meant-to-buy-arms-for-the-war-with-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰基辅（美联社）——据乌克兰安全部门报道，乌克兰一家军火公司的员工与国防部官员合谋挪用了近 4000 万美元，专门用于购买 10 万枚迫击炮弹，用于对俄战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-01-28/ukraine-says-corrupt-officials-stole-40-million-meant-to-buy-arms-for-the-war-with-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Jan 2024 08:59:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
